<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>구현<sp/>기준<sp/>원칙</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">이후<sp/>문서와<sp/>구현은<sp/>아래<sp/>원칙을<sp/>따른다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>기존<sp/>모듈을<sp/>&quot;대체&quot;하기보다<sp/>&quot;분해해서<sp/>재조립&quot;한다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`TextVisualizer`는<sp/>읽기<sp/>전용<sp/>표시<sp/>최적화가<sp/>기본값이다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>편집기<sp/>스택과<sp/>visual<sp/>스택의<sp/>장점만<sp/>취하고,<sp/>서로의<sp/>과한<sp/>책임은<sp/>들고<sp/>오지<sp/>않는다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>신규<sp/>구조는<sp/>향후<sp/>`TextLabel`,<sp/>`PreText`,<sp/>`Marquee`,<sp/>`rich<sp/>text<sp/>view`에도<sp/>확장<sp/>가능해야<sp/>한다.</highlight></codeline>
